      • DOOR_OPENED

        public static final Maze.SpecialEvent DOOR_OPENED
        When Chap uses a key to remove a block form the make. Removing a block is usually referred as opening a door, As it gives a better idea of what is happening. However, In the game logic the term block is used because once it is removed it can't go back. Therefore it isn't exactly a door as it can't be closed after it was unlocked with a key.
